  "title": "Dual Evaluation and Alignment",
  "concept": "When a performance is judged by two groups using different criteria—one scoring craft, the other scoring emotional impact—a work that scores high with both reveals it operates on multiple registers simultaneously, making it legible across evaluation systems.",
